<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2013/05/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>Cross.Messaging</id>
    <version>0.0.0</version>
    <authors>Denis Peshkov</authors>
    <owners>Denis Peshkov</owners>
    <copyright>Copyright 2026 Denis Peshkov</copyright>
    <projectUrl>https://github.com/denis-peshkov/Cross.Messaging</projectUrl>
    <repository url="https://github.com/denis-peshkov/Cross.Messaging.git" type="git" />
    <description>Helpers and services for sending notifications (email, SMS) and Telegram-related types, with DI-friendly configuration.</description>
    <tags>Email SMS Telegram Messaging SMTP MailKit Configuration DependencyInjection NetCore</tags>
    <readme>README.md</readme>
    <license type="file">LICENSE</license>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <releaseNotes><![CDATA[
- Email: added configurable `BccRecipients` in `MessagingEmail` section (`Name`, `Email`) for send flows.
- Email API: added priority overloads for `SendAsync(...)` and `SendAsyncWithContentIds(...)`, plus `SendAsync(...)` overloads without attachments.
- Tests: added category tags (`Unit`, `Integration`) and expanded service tests for new overloads.
- Documentation: updated README examples for API, categories, and category-based test execution.
]]></releaseNotes>
